description:
Was God’s Law abolished at Calvary? Although a topic of debate among Christians and even among denominations, the Bible is clear. God’s Law, a reflection of His character, is everlasting. Listen to this series to learn more about what #Adventists believe. 

To watch the full episode, paste the link into your browser: https://youtu.be/8wCwpWAaPlw
fulltitle: Did Jesus abolish the law when He died on the cross? #Short
